\cf0 Also in the header bar:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\li720\fi-720\sl264\slmult1\sa360\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can Control-click (or right-click) into the header view to bring up a menu of useful options.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can click into the title to rename the document.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can drag the icon shown next to the title in the same way that you can drag documents in the binder.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can drag a document from the binder into the header bar to load it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The square icon on the very right of the header view will split the editor, but we\'92ll come to that shortly.\
